            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1489557999,
            "creation_date": 1489557999,
            "body": "<p><code>setText<\/code> will update the text and repaint. However, if the text size is different layout might change so you will need a <code>revalidate<\/code> or <code>animateLayout*<\/code> call to reflow the UI otherwise things might not look as you'd expect in some situations.<\/p>\n\n<p>If you are on a separate thread (e.g. network callback that isn't on the EDT) you need a <code>callSerially<\/code> to avoid an EDT violation and hard to detect device bugs.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 42802195,
